high_descs: Head over to the cabinet by the trash can.
Place the dispenser in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Putting a soap dispenser in the trash can.

high_descs: Go right and then turn right again to face the toilet.
Pick the bottle on the left up from the back of the toilet.
Go right and then right again before turning right to face the green counter and trash can.
Put the bottle in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle on a toilet in a trash can.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the toilet tank
Pick up the lotion bottle on the left of the toilet tank
Carry the lotion bottle to the green trash can at the end of the counter on the floor
Place the lotion bottle in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Move a lotion bottle to the trash
